author: @Ruby_Skype
text: This is oppa third vlog in Milan, and I can hardly believe it. It's like a new world has opened up for him, and I'm so proud. Initially, I noticed his anxiety in the first vlogs, which I thought was natural since he was alone in an unfamiliar place. Now, he seems composed, and that makes me happy. His thoughts are beautiful and positive; he looks at people with affection and hugs everyone warmly. It's precious that he shares his experiences with us, and I find it very constructive. I enjoyed the show, as the fashion world is full of surprises, and I understand what Oppa means. JUNGWOO's outfit was a classic look with modern touches, while the photoshoot featured warmer shades that created beautiful contrasts. The goal of showcasing the style through the TOD collection has been successfully achieved, exuding an authentic classic aura that aligns with the TOD style. 👏🧡🤴
